{"tid":2102037,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不敵疫情 美國無印良品申請破產","createTime":"2020-07-10T07:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T08:02:15.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fbb65814f43c63a0e3a89f0ba2573d148b2dcd9d","tid":2102037,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:46:31.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕日本零售商良品計畫株式會社（Ryohin Keikaku）旗下無印良品（Muji），向來以極簡的居家用品聞名，但其美國部門最終也躲不過武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情侵襲，宣佈聲請破產。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》報導，根據1份文件顯示，美國無印良品已根據第11章破產法在德拉瓦州提出破產聲請，列出的資產及負債規模介於5000萬美元到1億美元之間，估計債權人數量落在200人到999人之間。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n根據聲明，在最近1個財年，美國業務的銷售額約佔良品計畫2.5%的收入，但過去3個財年來，美國業務一直處於虧損狀態，光去年就損失近1000萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3224229\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3224229&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwums70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=76e6559b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3224229&h=6c3cd06b\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3224229</a>"},{"pid":"3283398dfe4339e43f4da362c6c394c5f7afd828","tid":2102037,"uid":57671,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:02:15.000Z","msg":"聽日後日記得投票<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYaAEA4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYaAEA4.jpg&h=f73580f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aFBTrf5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaFBTrf5.jpg&h=5dd3e3aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JApxGPq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJApxGPq.jpg&h=a84e2f7f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b5KUU9r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb5KUU9r.jpg&h=59996e90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://